import React, { useState } from 'react'; const EmailTemplates = ({ onBack, onUseTemplate }) => { const [searchTerm, setSearchTerm] = useState(''); const [category, setCategory] = useState('all'); const categories = [ { id: 'all', label: 'All Templates' }, { id: 'followup', label: 'Follow-ups' }, { id: 'proposal', label: 'Grant Proposals' }, { id: 'meeting', label: 'Meeting Requests' }, { id: 'thankyou', label: 'Thank You Notes' }, { id: 'reminder', label: 'Reminders' } ]; const templates = [ { id: 1, title: 'Initial Grant Inquiry', category: 'proposal', description: 'Template for initial contact about grant opportunities', preview: 'Dear [Client Name], I hope this email finds you well. I am writing to inquire about potential grant opportunities...', icon: 'fas fa-handshake' }, { id: 2, title: 'Proposal Follow-up', category: 'followup', description: 'Follow up on submitted grant proposal', preview: 'Dear [Client Name], I wanted to follow up on the grant proposal we submitted on [Date]. Please let me know if you need any additional information...', icon: 'fas fa-sync' }, { id: 3, title: 'Meeting Request', category: 'meeting', description: 'Request a meeting to discuss grant strategy', preview: 'Dear [Client Name], I would like to schedule a meeting to discuss your grant strategy and upcoming opportunities...', icon: 'fas fa-calendar' }, { id: 4, title: 'Thank You Note', category: 'thankyou', description: 'Thank client for their collaboration', preview: 'Dear [Client Name], Thank you for your partnership and collaboration on the recent grant application...', icon: 'fas fa-heart' }, { id: 5, title: 'Deadline Reminder', category: 'reminder', description: 'Remind client about upcoming grant deadline', preview: 'Dear [Client Name], This is a friendly reminder that the grant application for [Grant Name] is due on [Date]...', icon: 'fas fa-bell' }, { id: 6, title: 'Budget Discussion', category: 'proposal', description: 'Template for discussing grant budget details', preview: 'Dear [Client Name], I have reviewed the budget requirements for the grant and would like to discuss the following items...', icon: 'fas fa-chart-pie' } ]; const filteredTemplates = templates.filter(template => { const matchesSearch = template.title.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()) || template.description.toLowerCase().includes(searchTerm.toLowerCase()); const matchesCategory = category === 'all' || template.category === category; return matchesSearch && matchesCategory; }); return (
